Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory365.png'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: 'Sis! What happened to the rabbits in the end?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'They stayed on the Moon.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'What were they going to do after they stayed on the Moon?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Um... What did they do... Since they loved carrots so much, I guess they must have planted a lot of carrots on the Moon.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'Okay! What did they do after that?', 4: '1'}

{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'After that... They were digging the ground in order to plant carrots. They dug and dug, until they found a carrot monster in the soil! It was formed by the spirits of all the carrots they ate!', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'A big monster! Then what? What happened to the rabbits...? Did the carrot monster eat them?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Um... Um... Right, the rabbits came together to build a robot called Iron Bunny. They were about to attack the carrot monster.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'The rabbits were so good... What happened after?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "Do you still want more...? Oh, right! Luna, it's about time for you to sleep. Otherwise I won't tell you stories tomorrow.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'Are you going to tell me more stories tomorrow?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Of course... But you need to sleep first.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'Sure. Luna will be a good girl. Good night, Sis!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Goodnight, Luna... Have a nice dream. Tomorrow will be a new day.', 4: '2'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStorySandNew.prefab', 2: '2'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory588.jpg'}
{3: 'Raging gravitational waves are tearing apart the tiny lab relentlessly. The interval between waves is quickly decreasing, approaching the critical point.'}
{3: 'Decomposed buildings keep falling around. The giant Omega Weapon has completed its mission and gets buried under the debris.'}
{3: '—The imprisoned agent is no longer here.'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStorySandNew.prefab'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory593.jpg'}

{1: '1', 3: 'The wrecked zero-point engine emits a blazing blue light from the center of the gravity waves. Around them floats a white figure that seems completely unaffected by the gravitational waves.'}
{3: "The pale flesh wiggles around the zero-point engine, trying to crawl onto the white figure's body."}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'You too are a pathetic creation. Your fate was twisted from the very beginning...', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Luna allows it to wrap around her, but the moment it touches Luna, it turns into crimson ash and dissolves away.'}
{3: 'The blue glow of the zero-point engine is turning incandescent white, warning everyone that the gravitational waves will soon explode and destroy everything on the ground.'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'Is this the pure destructive power brought by science...? Let me harness this power.', 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryGanRanNew.prefab', 2: '2', 3: '1'}
{3: 'Luna raises her right hand and gathers all the Punishing Virus from the entire lunar base.'}

{3: 'The condensed Punishing Virus gradually forms a hardened spherical shell, encasing the wrecked zero-point engine and Luna herself. Meanwhile, chaotic and destructive gravitational waves also slowly gather around Luna.'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: "I'm going back... to where Sis is.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Luna gently holds the Frog charm in her scarred right hand. She rests it on the safest place near her chest.'}
{3: 'The concentrated gravitational waves send the Punishing Virus sphere afloat before it disappears in a blazing light.'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryGanRanNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory394.jpg'}
{1: '1', 3: 'The white-haired girl is moving alone in the wilderness. She suddenly stops.'}
{3: "As if she has heard something, she raises her head slightly to look at the night sky. It's almost dawn."}
{3: 'A meteor suddenly bursts into the sky and slowly descends.'}
{3: 'The Ascendant named Alpha takes a few baffled steps. She then quickly sprints toward the sunrise.'}
